EXECUTIVE SUMMARY\par
Viraz is a revolutionary dual-sided platform connecting Sponsors (advertisers) and Users (audience) through an interactive, reward-based advertising ecosystem. The core innovation is the "Billboard" \f1\endash  a discovery page for interactive "Rooms" where users earn Convertible Accumulated Points (CAP) for genuine engagement. This creates a high-attention environment for sponsors and a rewarding experience for users, effectively transforming passive advertising into an interactive economy.\par
