1.0 PLATFORM OVERVIEW\par
1.1 Vision Statement\par
To create the world's first engagement economy where attention is fairly rewarded and advertising becomes genuinely interactive and valuable for all parties.\par
\par
1.2 Platform Mission\par
Connect brands with highly engaged audiences through rewarding interactions, while providing users with a meaningful way to earn from their attention and participation.\par
\par
1.3 Key Value Propositions\par
For Users:\par
\par
Earn real value (CAP) for everyday engagement\par
\par
Discover new products and brands interactively\par
\par
Influence brand decisions through suggestions\par
\par
Build reputation and influence\par
\par
Purchase products with earned points\par
\par
For Sponsors:\par
\par
Pay only for verified, genuine engagement\par
\par
Receive direct feedback from target audience\par
\par
Build authentic brand communities\par
\par
Access detailed analytics and insights\par
\par
Convert engaged users into customers\par
\par
