2.5.2 CAP Earning Mechanisms\par
\par
Dynamic CAP Valuation:\par
\par
text\par
Base CAP Value = Total Sponsor Deposits / Total CAP in Circulation\par
Example:\par
- Total sponsor deposits: $100,000\par
- Total CAP issued: 20,000,000\par
- Base CAP Value: $0.005 per CAP\par
Earning Safeguards:\par
\par
Daily earning caps based on user rank\par
\par
Verification requirements for high earnings\par
\par
Anti-fraud monitoring\par
\par
Suspicious activity limits\par
\par
Cooldown periods between actions\par
\par
