4.0 ECONOMIC MODEL & CAP SYSTEM\par
4.1 CAP Economics Framework\par
Core Principles:\par
\par
CAP derives value from sponsor deposits\par
\par
Value should be stable but can fluctuate\par
\par
Users should be incentivized to earn and spend\par
\par
Sponsors should see clear ROI\par
\par
Platform sustainability through transaction fees\par
\par
4.2 Dynamic CAP Valuation\par
Valuation Formula:\par
\par
text\par
CAP Value = (Total Sponsor Deposits + Platform Reserve) / Total CAP in Circulation\par
\par
Where:\par
- Total Sponsor Deposits = All fiat money deposited for campaigns\par
- Platform Reserve = 10% of deposits held for stability\par
- Total CAP in Circulation = All CAP earned but not spent\par
Example Scenarios:\par
\par
Scenario\tab Sponsor Deposits\tab CAP in Circulation\tab CAP Value\par
Launch\tab $10,000\tab 1,000,000\tab $0.01\par
Growth\tab $100,000\tab 15,000,000\tab $0.0067\par
Maturity\tab $1,000,000\tab 80,000,000\tab $0.0125\par
